{"tid":21040,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"P 牌 問 題","createTime":"2016-12-03T15:39:34.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T16:52:01.000Z","uid":53866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fe29e81e5d440180eb5468bb00c0f7f32d816e9c","tid":21040,"uid":53866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:39:34.000Z","msg":"考到牌1個月，上28睇中部121，淨係自己睇無上架，星期一會去同車主交收<br />\n但問題就黎啦！<br />\n<br />\n1. 燕梳問左快而保quote價 7500$ 墊底費好貴，但唔緊要 旨在出到部車，如果星期一一早去搞，係咪即刻可以拎到cover note? 保費係咪都要即刻全數比定係過左戶先俾？ <br />\n<br />\n2. 試過部車， 落brake要去到一半先有反應，係咪代表迫力皮已經準備打柴？ 定係brake油出左問題？ 如果係拎去車房換的話，大慨幾多錢左右？<br />\n<br />\n3. 可唔可以推介有咩shell既油卡夠抵？<br />\n<br />\n4. 拎車後都會裝隻車cam，$1000筆直巴打有無平靚正既推介？ <br />\n<br />\n仲有好多問題，不過最大問題係沙田交收要自己一個揸番去旺角，唔想一拎車就出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打教路一下p牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c2cc6d45de289ccae41f4b0d2882bd61cc9051","tid":21040,"uid":42571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:46:23.000Z","msg":"P牌留名 都係買車無耐 渣左半個月 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f94bed7a71c3b2196d928b8b7477907174ad61b","tid":21040,"uid":11733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:46:42.000Z","msg":"我第一日攞車自己由深水埗揸去觀塘再番大尾督夜晚再過北角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  攞左牌 過兩日就出左部腳車"},{"pid":"b255a86508e8bf7000b7fa5f5160167498702bad","tid":21040,"uid":11733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:47:02.000Z","msg":"唔熟路就開gps 啦"},{"pid":"be772a064e009167c310e69e47fb5f54202f5e1d","tid":21040,"uid":53510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:50:26.000Z","msg":"燕梳要比晒，基本上係即刻出到cover note <br />\n<br />\nBrake 就去車房驗啦，點會就咁就知咩事"},{"pid":"3481bc48b3a766b2fcd508669dd9c80313c18923","tid":21040,"uid":53510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:51:57.000Z","msg":"油咭冇<br />\n<br />\n車cam我用緊部2舊水⋯⋯拍到錄到就得，唔洗靚"},{"pid":"5f79c8c1eb63b80b44d8ca10dcb6e30430614757","tid":21040,"uid":53866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:46:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>燕梳要比晒，基本上係即刻出到cover note <br />\n<br />\nBrake 就去車房驗啦，點會就咁就知咩事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果最後唔買有無得退番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb64db5aac42c219e85c90afae9d9547b0e80ad4","tid":21040,"uid":34971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T22:34:06.000Z","msg":"cover note就係預一段時間畀你過戶先<br />\n<br />\n另外想問問剛考完牌嘅大家<br />\npass咗之後隔幾耐先拎到車牌？"},{"pid":"ff4f35cf8452ad7b4938095052ab2d688b5cbbd7","tid":21040,"uid":48088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T23:26:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>燕梳要比晒，基本上係即刻出到cover note <br />\n<br />\nBrake 就去車房驗啦，點會就咁就知咩事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果最後唔買有無得退番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無....所以我覺得你應該上架驗左先搞燕梳....<br />\n<br />\n我都係楂 121....自動波車係要踩深少少先會開始有反應<br />\n同棍仔有少少分別.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a09266fe7ef80fe72138710d7a43b426c5ed235b","tid":21040,"uid":53510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T01:14:42.000Z","msg":"燕梳係有得退既，不過一定唔會退足"},{"pid":"7895920896a8011de40c397ffb555274b2f0fcc0","tid":21040,"uid":40999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T01:22:05.000Z","msg":"係28買車唔驗車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打部121幾多年車？<br />\n未落訂我建議你真係驗一驗好啲，買錯到時整車整到你hihi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114f0309cec5c7ebed915cc4536f2da0fafd490f","tid":21040,"uid":53866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T02:03:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係2